{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Node.replaceChild","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI\"><code>baseURI</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes\"><code>childNodes</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild\"><code>firstChild</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>isConnected</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/lastChild\"><code>lastChild</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling\"><code>nextSibling</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeName\"><code>nodeName</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeType\"><code>nodeType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeValue\"><code>nodeValue</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/ownerDocument\"><code>ownerDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/parentElement\"><code>parentElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/parentNode\"><code>parentNode</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/previousSibling\"><code>previousSibling</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/textContent\"><code>textContent</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/appendChild\"><code>appendChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/cloneNode\"><code>cloneNode()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/compareDocumentPosition\"><code>compareDocumentPosition()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/contains\"><code>contains()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/hasChildNodes\"><code>hasChildNodes()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/insertBefore\"><code>insertBefore()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isDefaultNamespace\"><code>isDefaultNamespace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isEqualNode\"><code>isEqualNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSameNode\"><code>isSameNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSupported\"><code>isSupported()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupNamespaceURI\"><code>lookupNamespaceURI()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupPrefix\"><code>lookupPrefix()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/normalize\"><code>normalize()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild\"><code>removeChild()</code></a></li><li><em><code>replaceChild()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Zusammenfassung","isH3":true,"content":"<p><strong>Die <code>Node.replaceChild()</code></strong>-Methode ersetzt den&nbsp;Kind-Knoten (<code>child node)</code>&nbsp;<u>innerhalb</u> des gegebenen Eltern-Knotens (<code>parent node</code>)&nbsp;durch einen anderen.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><em>replacedNode</em> = <em>parentNode</em>.replaceChild(<em>newChild</em>, <em>oldChild</em>);\n</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>newChild</code> ist der neue, <code>oldChild</code> der zu ersetzende Knoten. Falls er bereits im DOM vorhanden ist, wird er zuerst von dort entfernt.</li>\n <li><code>oldChild</code> ist der zu ersetzende Knoten.</li>\n <li><code>replacedNode</code> ist der ersetzte Knoten, also der selbe wie <code>oldChild</code>.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Beispiel","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">// &lt;div&gt;\n//  &lt;span id=\"childSpan\"&gt;foo bar&lt;/span&gt;\n// &lt;/div&gt;\n\n// erzeuge einen leeren Element-Knoten\n// ohne ID, Attribute oder Inhalt\nvar sp1 = document.createElement(\"span\");\n\n// setze sein id Attribut auf 'newSpan'\nsp1.setAttribute(\"id\", \"newSpan\");\n\n// Inhalt für das neue Element erzeugen\nvar sp1_content = document.createTextNode(\"new replacement span element.\");\n\n// den erzeugten Inhalt an das Element anhängen\nsp1.appendChild(sp1_content);\n\n// Referenz auf den zu ersetzenden Knoten erzeugen\nvar sp2 = document.getElementById(\"childSpan\");\nvar parentDiv = sp2.parentNode;\n\n// den existierenden Knoten sp2 mit dem neuen Span-Element sp1 ersetzen\nparentDiv.replaceChild(sp1, sp2);\n\n// Ergebnis:\n// &lt;div&gt;\n//   &lt;span id=\"newSpan\"&gt;new replacement span element.&lt;/span&gt;\n// &lt;/div&gt;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Spezifikation","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/REC-DOM-Level-1/level-one-core.html#method-replaceChild\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 1 Core: replaceChild</a></p>\n\n<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-785887307\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: replaceChild</a></p>\n\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Die Node.replaceChild()-Methode ersetzt den Kind-Knoten (child node) innerhalb des gegebenen Eltern-Knotens (parent node) durch einen anderen.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.replaceChild()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.replaceChild()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.replaceChild","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.replaceChild","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.replaceChild()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"element.replaceChild","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Node.replaceChild","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Node.replaceChild","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.replaceChild()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/node/replacechild","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/node/replacechild/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild","title":"Node.replaceChild"}],"pageTitle":"Node.replaceChild - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}